# ml/data/splits/ - Train/Val/Test Splits
#
# PURPOSE:
#     Store dataset split definitions (train, validation, test).
#     These are JSON files referencing samples in processed/.
#
# REFERENCED BY:
#     - scripts/prepare_imda_data.py - Creates splits
#     - scripts/train_lora.py - Loads train/val splits
#     - scripts/evaluate.py - Loads test split
#
# FILES:
#     - train.json - 80% of samples (training)
#     - val.json - 10% of samples (validation during training)
#     - test.json - 10% of samples (final evaluation)
#
# FORMAT:
#     [
#         {"audio": "path/to/audio.wav", "transcript": "text here"},
#         ...
#     ]
